attachments.title: AZ Hack Day Hackathon
attachments.text: Hackathon Details: We are excited to kick off our inaugural single day hackathon, AZ Hack Day! All backgrounds and skill levels are encouraged to participate. If you have never done a hackathon before this is a great one to make your first. Since this is a single day event and we want as much hacking as possible, I will coordinate team forming beforehand.
